A1.content: Shipping and Assembly Cost Form Instructions

A3.content: To provide your customer with an accurate quotation, please fill the yellow cells in sheet Transport & Assembly.

A6.content: - Indicate the additional volume that might be required to secure the shipment.

A7.content: - In case of a local delivery, insert the number of kilometers to the delivery address.

A8.content: - If needed, select another truck for the delivery.

A11.content: - Indicate the extra time required for the apprentice to perform his/her work.

A12.content: - Indicate the extra time required for the carpenter to perform his/her work.

A13.content: - Indicate the risk factor added to the total assembly cost (10% by default).

A15.content: Review and Submit by clicking on

C15.content: at the top of the window.
